Postcode,Anywhere,is,an,information,as,a,service,provider,offering,over,separate,web,services,covering,a,broad,range,of,business,efficiency,tools,for,address,and,data,capture,validation,and,cleansing,to,geo,coding,mapping,and,route,planning,and,optimization,The,Geocoding,API,allows,users,to,geocode,UK,addresses,and,postcodes,and,integrate,them,into,their,websites,and,applications,as,well,as,coordinates,from,around,the,world,Users,can,also,retrieve,the,names,of,nearby,places,The,API,uses,a,number,of,protocols,including,REST,SOAP,and,XML,RPC,Responses,can,be,formatted,in,XML,JSON,CSV,HTML,and,PDF